+{"id":"br-r37-c1-3854183f","title":"Make conformance dashboard golden output deterministic","description":"testing-golden-artifacts found that scripts/generate_conformance_dashboard.py declares deterministic=true but writes datetime.now() into generated_at_utc and builds run_id from the current epoch timestamp. Re-running the generator changes artifacts/conformance/latest/conformance_dashboard_v1.json without any input change, which defeats exact golden comparison and freshness reviews. Fix by deriving stable metadata from input artifact content and add a regression test that generate_dashboard() returns identical output across repeated calls. UUID: 3854183f-664f-490a-9848-232d701ac063.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-28T19:53:29Z","created_by":"codex","updated_at":"2026-04-28T19:55:41Z","closed_at":"2026-04-28T19:55:41Z","close_reason":"Conformance dashboard now derives generated_at_utc from stable input artifacts and run_id from a content hash; added an exact repeated-generation regression test.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
